9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Bāhubali: The Epic | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"When a mysterious child is found by a tribal couple near a roaring waterfall, they raise him as their own. As he grows, Sivudu is drawn to the world beyond the cliffs, where he discovers the ancient kingdom of Mahishmati, ruled by a cruel tyrant, haunted by rebellion, and bound to his past. What begins as a quest for love soon unravels a legacy of betrayal, sacrifice, and a forgotten prince."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/108553/b-hubali-the-epic"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Bāhubali: The Epic"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"When a mysterious child is found by a tribal couple near a roaring waterfall, they raise him as their own. As he grows, Sivudu is drawn to the world beyond the cliffs, where he discovers the ancient kingdom of Mahishmati, ruled by a cruel tyrant, haunted by rebellion, and bound to his past. What begins as a quest for love soon unravels a legacy of betrayal, sacrifice, and a forgotten prince."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/108553/b-hubali-the-epic"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/z9YIo2qscyaXYgRqIdRJtND3bw8.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Bāhubali: The Epic"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"When a mysterious child is found by a tribal couple near a roaring waterfall, they raise him as their own. As he grows, Sivudu is drawn to the world be